transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling customer service. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, I'm a patient. My name is Joseph Rubino, R-U-B-I-N-O.

Speaker 1: I was on automatic refill, and I'd like to cancel that and just call when I need something.

Speaker 2: Okay. Can I have your birthday and zip code, please?

Speaker 1: July 7, 1975.

Speaker 2: Okay. Your account is paused.

Speaker 1: Whenever you're ready to order, you can just call in and place the order,

Speaker 2: or you can do it online with the doctor.

Speaker 1: All right. Thank you very much.

Speaker 2: You're welcome. Have a good one. Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye.
